Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}早上好  太太\NWell, mornin', little missus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}想和敬畏上帝的男人们共进早餐吗\NCare for some breakfast with some god-fearing men?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.27,0:02:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么了\NHey, hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不想跟我们玩玩吗\NDon't you want to spend a little time with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别听他的  女士\NDon't listen to him, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我到处都找不到你\NYou weren't anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你好像都没有上床睡觉\NDidn't even look like you came to bed for one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我有了个主意\NI had this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是挖掘机\NIt's a dredge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是蒸汽式挖掘机\NIt's a steam dredge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在过来的路上了\NIt's on its way to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}随时可能到\NShould be here any day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们得把它改造成蒸汽铲\NWe'll have to convert it to a steam shovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}今早我突然想到\NHad a notion just this mornin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可以做一个底盘\NI could build an undercarriage--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你得睡觉  吃东西  或者...\NYou need to sleep and eat or...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我不知道要做什么\NI don't know what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不明白\NYou don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你最好带威廉回家吧\NBetter take William on along home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他不该出来  你也是\NShouldn't be out here. You neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会回家的  你走吧\NI'll be along. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}只要七条菱形道岔就能到达顶峰\NI know we can reach the summit in seven diagonal cuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这叫做"之字形路"  对吧\NThey're called "Switchbacks," all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很熟悉这一概念\NI'm familiar with the concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是工程师  博汉南\NI'm an engineer, Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}总工程师\NChief engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你先别急着给我下命令\NBefore you start givin' me orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是为杜兰特先生工作的\Nit's Mr. Durant I work for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为联太公司工作\NYou work for the Union Pacific.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们的任务是铺好铁路\NOur job is to get the railroad movin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我需要十二个人帮忙做出加固底盘\NI need a dozen men to help fashion a reinforced chassis
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-这样就可以  -你需要\N- so I can-- - You need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}先生们\NGentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南先生刚给我分配了工作  还有你的\NMr. Bohannon was just tellin' me what my job is. Yours too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}挖掘机随时都可能到  而我们还没有准备好\NDredge'll be here any day now and we ain't ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.59,0:04:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-他要求十个人  -是十二个\N- He is requesting 10 men... - 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}停止筑墙  去组装零件\NTo be taken off their labor on the wall to assemble parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.67,0:04:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有造一辆车\NAnd build a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们有没有专门技术  来向工人们展示\NAnd do we have the expertise to show the men
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-要怎么做  -我有个想法\N- how this is done? - I got a notion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}想法啊\NA notion? Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我需要借助德兰尼先生的专业知识\NBut I'll need Mr. Delaney's know-how.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你说呢\NWell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可以\NIt can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果十二个人可以将就的话\NIf you settle for 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.51,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}等一下\NHold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们走\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.86,0:06:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我让你们等一下\NI said stop the train right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该死\NDamn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不好意思\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你坐下\NSit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让大伙儿下车\NPull the men off your train.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们有新任务\NThey've been reassigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-谁说的  -我说的\N- On whose say-so? - Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么不让我们走\NWhat's this with pullin' my men?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}带十个最厉害的下车  包括你\NTake your ten best off the train, and you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-我需要你来负责  -负责什么\N- I need you in charge. - Charge of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你要么一起来要么走人\NEither you come or I take 'em without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不把滑动装置搞定就没法用了\NDead in the water until you get that slide off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}维吉尔\NVirgil!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南先生\NMr. Bohannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这些人不是该去铲石头吗\NShouldn't these men be out shovelin' rocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也这么觉得\NI been thinkin' the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好  我们把两辆货车\NAll right, we're gonna take them two freight trucks
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:06:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安放到铁轨上\Nand set 'em on the rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这样就可以运挖掘机了\NThey'll hold the platform for the dredge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你以为我们有钢铁厂吗\NYou think we got an ironworks here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-这里又不是芝加哥  -因为重量增加\N- We ain't in Chicago. - You best build new bolsters
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所以最好用新垫板和中心立轴\Nand kingpins for the extra weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}今早我看了下  应该是这样的\NI had a look this mornin', figure it's somethin' like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你明白吗  我们只修坏掉的东西\NYou hear me? We fix what's broke and that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}根本没人手帮我做那个\NI barely got the manpower for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人手我给你带来了\NOh, I brought you the manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说的是技术工人\NI'm talkin' about skilled labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-帕萨姆  -我的人可以学\N- Psalms? - My men'll learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们有人以前是种地轧棉花的呢\NSome of them worked on ploughs and cotton gins where they from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}火车车厢可不是轧棉机\NRailroad cars ain't cotton gins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你应该听到他说的话了吧\NAnd I think you heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们可以学\NThey can learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}眼见为实\NI'll believe it when I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.06,0:07:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}准备开工\NGet her in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那里那个人\NMan right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以为你只擅长挖渠开沟\NThinks all you good for is diggin' ditches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你想证明他错了吗\NYou wanna prove him wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你看到我时看到的是什么\NI know what you see when you look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我看未必\NDoubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杀害埃兰的凶手\NThe man who killed Elam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.84,0:08:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但那不是埃兰\NBut that wasn't Elam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你我认识的那个人  永远不会回来了\NThe one you and me knew. He never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就只想说这么多\NThat's all I'm gonna say about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不再多说\NNow or ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会让我的人在维吉尔手下好好干活\NI see to it my crew give Virgil no reason to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}安放车轮时注意安全\NY'all watch your feet mountin' them wheels now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你现在想好要怎么办了吗\NYou thought about what you're gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是说  你想回家了吗\NI mean, will you go home now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}圣路易斯\NSt. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}圣路易斯\NSt. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是我家\NThat's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但我在那没家人了\NBut I got no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没有家人  一无所有\NNo one and nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  不是的\NNo, that ain't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你识字\NYou can read.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会讲话\NYou talk nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}脸蛋也漂亮\NYou got a pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不用做妓女的\NYou don't have to be a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你可以找更好的职业\NYou can be somethin' better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你不明白\NYou don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不做这个可能会更糟  这我明白\NCould be a lot worse, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在我嫁给埃兰之前\NBefore I was with Elam--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}埃兰\NElam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我帮你在夏安镇找到工作前  和我住\NStay with me till we find you somethin' to do in Cheyenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们一起想办法\NWe'll think on it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-早上好  -早上好\N- Mornin'. - Mornin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}您的电报\NFor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们在内布拉斯加找到了海柯德的尸体\NThey found Heckard's body in Nebraska.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}躺在铁路边上\NBy the side of the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有人打碎了他脑袋\NSomebody bashed his head in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是  长官\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们是在怎样的一个地方  艾特伍德\NWhat kind of a place have we found ourselves in, Atwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.11,0:10:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}美国联邦法警的性命\NWhere the life of a U.S. Marshal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会被一只妄自尊大的癞蛤蟆\Ncan be snuffed out at the whim of an arrogant,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}凭一时意气夺走\Npompous, self-important toad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特吗\NDurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}源头不治理\NShit flows downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}哪来清河水\NFrom the headwaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}娜奥米\NNaomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}驾\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}站住\NHold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉海彻神父他女儿来了\NTell Father Hatch his daughter's at the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}海彻兄弟\NBrother Hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}吁\NHo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}感觉我们走了很久了\NFeels a long time since we've been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}并没有\NIt wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但感觉很像\NFeels like it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}赞美上帝\NOh, god be praised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看看他\NOh, look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南兄弟\NBrother Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-海彻神父  -进来呀\N- Father Hatch. - Well, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-干嘛站在外面  -主教呢\N- Why are we stayin' out here? - The bishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他早不在了  不用担心他\NAh. He's long gone, you needn't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们赶了那么多路\NNow, you've been traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}又累又饿吧\NYou're tired and hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.02,0:13:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你妈一定很高兴\NYour momma's gonna be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}驾\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在这等着\NWait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}作为死刑犯  你看起来很轻松嘛\NYou look rather cavalier for a man who's set to hang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你很喜欢这么目无法纪吗\NIs it your habit to take the law of the land so lightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.87,0:14:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个州长跑到这种地方\NAin't the usual thing for a Governor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}跟一个死刑犯谈话  真不寻常\Nto come down here and conversate with condemned fugitives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我问你是不是目无法纪\NI'm askin' if you hold the law in contempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.93,0:14:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}法律和我互相为难对方\NThe law and me have been at each other pretty hard
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}已经很久啦\Nfor a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们互相了解\NWe know each other well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你有特殊的技能  斯诺先生\NYou have certain skills, Mr. Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我也许需要你的技能\NI may have need for those skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}问题是你能否把那些技能\NThe question is whether you can put them to use for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}传授给别人\Nother than yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这我可从来没试过\NI have never tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你替我工作  我救你的命怎么样\NWhat if it were worth your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你发誓执行怀俄明州的法律\NDo you swear to enforce the law of Wyoming,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其文字和精神\Nits letter and its spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}执行公务  不存偏见\Nwithout prejudice of persons in pursuance of your duties?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是的  我发誓\NRight, yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那么你是新法警了\NThen you're our new marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很多人都会吃惊的\NLots of individuals would be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}夏安镇有很多其他地方的通缉犯\NCheyenne's full of men wanted elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}逃保者  亡命徒\NBail jumpers, fugitives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}铁路工人中还有契约自由人\NAlso indentured freedmen among the railroad workers,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}游民无赖\Nvagrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特几年没付过他们债券了\NDurant hasn't paid their bond in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也就是说他们也是非法的\NThat means they're illegal too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要你逮捕所有这些人\NI want you to arrest them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:16:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-我需要几位副官  -就是他们了\N- Gonna need some deputies. - Take those.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}该死  伙计们  今天是你们的幸运日\NDamn, boys, it's your lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}敢违反我的命令\NTravel one inch outside my orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我就亲手吊死你\NI'll tie the noose myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别担心  州长\NNot to worry, Governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}能为你做事很荣幸\NMy honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}绅士地握个手吧\NAs a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}从这些人开始\NYou start with those.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}夏洛特会做饭  洗衣服  做家务\NCharlotte can cook, wash, keep house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她很会算账\NDoes her figures like anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}擅长读写\NShe can read and write like nobody's business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}大家能看出她是个体面的人\NFolks can see she's a respectable person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会给你一身替换的衣服\NWe'll get you a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会在这给你找点活儿干\NI'll find something for you to do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我简直不能想象你经历了什么\NCan't even imagine what you've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢...\NThank--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没事的\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}谢谢您\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他的眼睛像他爸\NHe's got eyes like his papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他难道没继承博汉南兄弟那双漂亮的眼睛吗\NDon't he have brother Bohannon's pretty eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你居然敢说我老公眼睛漂亮\NHow dare you say that about my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以丝特已经有自己的男人了\NEsther's got her own beau.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}迈克尔·杜恩兄弟\NBrother Michael Doone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他的眼睛好像晒太阳的老公牛似的\NHe's got eyes like an old ox sittin' in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}姑娘们\NGirls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这可是娜奥米回家来的第一顿饭\NThis is Naomi's first meal home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她跟她们在一起很开心\NShe's happy to be among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}她想念这种生活\NShe's missed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这是事实\NThat's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想我猜的到是什么让你离开夏安镇\NWell, I can only guess at what's brought you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}回到了这里\Nback from Cheyenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是难道没有什么能让你留下的理由吗\NBut is there any good reason you shouldn't stay on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们俩一起\NBoth of you, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}留在我们身边\NWith us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在这里我说了算\NI have authority here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可以帮你在公理会说说话\NI can smooth your way with the congregation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}大家会欢迎你的\NYou will be made welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也许达森主教真的是对的\NPerhaps bishop dutson was right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么说\NHow's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个正义之人所能有的最高期许都能\NOnly that everything a righteous man could ever want
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在这里找到\Nis here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你那话什么意思  达森走了  去哪了\NWhat'd you mean, Dutson's gone? Gone where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为布里格姆·杨\NBrigham Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}去了犹他州\NTo Utah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你父亲希望我们留下来\NYour father wants us to stay on for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.68,0:19:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还没明确表态是否愿意\NYou still ain't said if that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我连想都不愿想回去的事\NI can't think about goin' back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.67,0:19:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}娜奥米\NNaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们在这里过得更好\NWe're better off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我和威廉  别跟我说你没看出来\NMe and William, and don't say that you don't see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你在夏安镇过得不好\NYou ain't had it easy in Cheyenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道的  行吗\NI know that, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我真的知道\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但夏安镇也不会一直如此的\NBut it ain't always gonna be Cheyenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}铁路会延续  我们也\NThe railroad'll move on, we'll--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不是因为夏安镇\NThis isn't about Cheyenne!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我洗去了你衣上的血迹\NI washed the blood off of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}洗去了一个被你杀掉的\NWashed the blood off of you of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你很敬爱的人的血迹\Nthat you killed, that you loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.54,0:20:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我永远不会忘记\NI ain't forgettin' that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这就是你\NThat's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真实的你\NThat's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}终点到了  各位\NEnd of the line, folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}夏安镇  终点站\NCheyenne. End of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}通缉令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}让我瞧瞧  老伙计\NWhat we got here, old timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:21:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们几个\NY'all go ahead around
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:22:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}从那些货车后面绕过去  懂吗\Nthe back side of those wagons over there, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.87,0:22:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-是  长官  -你听到命令了\N- Yes, sir. - You heard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}起\NHup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错  哥们儿\NThat's it, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}铁匠铺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把它对齐\NEven that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}起\NHup!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}往上点  哥们儿\NGet it on up, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}放进去\NGet it in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错  各位\NThat's it, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所有人\NAll you men!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}看来你们中有些人是通缉犯\NIt appears some of you are wanted by the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有些是没有债券的非法劳工\NElse you're here on bonds that ain't been paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是来逮捕你们  主持正义的\NI am here to see that y'all are brought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们少给我点麻烦  这事也就好过去\NLess trouble you give me, easier it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.46,0:22:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当然啦  我也不怕麻烦\N'course, I don't mind trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}所有这些人  所有的\NAll of these men, all of 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都是联太公司的合法劳工\NAre legitimate employees of the Union Pacific Railroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}长官\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.29,0:23:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}通缉  悬赏200美元\N维吉尔·法恩斯沃思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}维吉尔·法恩斯沃思\NVirgil Farnsworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在纽约被通缉\NWanted in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.33,0:23:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那是一次酒吧斗殴\NIt was a bar fight
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.65,0:23:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就在波威里街上[纽约街名]\Ndown at the Bowery.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}其他肇事者走开了\NOther guy walked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.34,0:23:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你们难道不考虑这点吗\NDon't that count for nothin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}达奇·杜弗雷\NDutch Dufray.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.99,0:23:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在博爱城[费城别称]武装抢劫\NArmed robbery in the city of brotherly love!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}任何阻拦我们的人\NAnybody gets in our way,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一并抓起来\Nyou arrest them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在...瞧瞧还有谁\NNow...Who do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}朱利叶斯·汉凯\NJulius Hankey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}瞧瞧那孩子跑的\NLook at that boy run.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.60,0:23:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}伊诺克·布尔\NEnoch Buell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}帕萨姆·杰克逊\NPsalms Jackson.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}杜兰特没给我付钱\NDurant didn't pay my bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么不逮捕他\NWhy don't you arrest him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.22,0:23:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有可能会哦\NIt might come to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.17,0:23:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}走\NMove.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.55,0:23:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}走吧\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:23:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}就这样  就这些了\NThat's it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}把这些人都抓起来  先生们  跟我来\NRound up the goodies, gentlemen. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.07,0:24:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}滚出去  没错\NGet outta here! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.32,0:24:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}放什么屁  我没抢过任何人\NWhat kind of cra-- I never robbed nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.61,0:24:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}至少没在俄亥俄州抢过\NNot in Ohio anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.59,0:24:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我才不在乎那张通缉令上写了什么呢\NI don't care what the poster says!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.01,0:24:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们会把你拖到法官面前的\NWe gonna drag you down to the judge,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.36,0:24:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你到他面前去叨叨吧\Nand you can talk his ear off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.48,0:24:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}狗娘养的\NSon of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.63,0:25:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}字母"I"是...\N"I" Is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.91,0:25:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}岛...岛屿\NIs--is-land?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.70,0:25:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-岛屿  -岛屿\N- Island. - Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.15,0:25:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}岛屿坐落在海上\NThat sits in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.35,0:25:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}字母"J"是...\N"J" is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.34,0:25:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}胡...狼\NJack-kal?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.52,0:25:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}-胡狼  -胡狼\N- Jackal! - Jackal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.72,0:25:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}胡狼从树上蹿出\NThat springs from the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.87,0:25:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}字母"K"是...\N"K" is a...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.26,0:25:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}露丝  我有事相求\NRuth! I'm in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.61,0:25:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}米奇\NMickey?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.28,0:25:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我需要一个地方容身  一个藏身之地\NI need a place to stay, to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.21,0:25:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我被通缉了\NI'm a wanted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.31,0:25:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们现在来追捕我了\NThey're coming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.33,0:25:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你瞧我这儿有个孩子呢\NYou see I have a child here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.91,0:25:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你居然带着一把枪到礼拜的地方来\NYou come with a gun to a place of worship?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.84,0:25:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这也是我救了你一命的地方\NThe place I saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.87,0:25:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}至于枪的问题\NAs for a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.03,0:25:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}假如你帮我  我就不打算用它了\NI've no mind to use it if you help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.63,0:25:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没有地方藏你\NI have nowhere to hide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.43,0:26:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这次我要亲自上了  伙计们\NI believe I'll take this myself, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.49,0:26:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}真他妈漂亮啊\NHot damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.89,0:26:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我以后得常来教堂\NI got to go to church more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.39,0:26:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有什么可以效劳的吗\NCan I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.92,0:26:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我可以想到成千上百种你效劳的方式\NWell, I can think of a thousand ways you could,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.61,0:26:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}亲爱的  但是这次\Ndarlin', but for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.06,0:26:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们在找这些人\Nwe're just lookin' for these men.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.96,0:26:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里只有我和孩子\NIt's just me and the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.94,0:26:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你要知道对联邦法警撒谎\NYou know lyin' to a federal marshal
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.39,0:26:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不仅仅是罪过  而且违法\Nain't just a sin, it's a felony.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.84,0:26:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里没人\NThere's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.56,0:26:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不信你自己看\NYou see for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.88,0:27:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我还没看后面呢\NI ain't seen what's back there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.72,0:27:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}满意了吗\NSatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.52,0:28:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我这人不会轻易满意\NI don't satisfy easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会为了你和宝宝回来的\NI'm comin' back for you and the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.81,0:30:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}光说没用\NDon't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.03,0:30:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我会的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.16,0:30:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那就等你回来时再见吧\NI'll see you when you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.58,0:30:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}好的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.79,0:31:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}帕默小姐把你打扮的很漂亮\NMiss Palmer done you up real nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.66,0:31:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这身打扮能让你觉得不同\NIt can make you feel different.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.20,0:31:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}感觉更好\NBetter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.69,0:31:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我都忘记这种感觉了\NI'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.95,0:31:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}帕默夫人让我在饭厅做事\NMrs. Palmer put me to work in the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.05,0:31:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}可笑的是你整天服侍人进餐自己就没胃口了\NFunny how you lose your appetite servin' food all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.03,0:32:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有些事我不得不跟你讲\NThere's somethin' I have to say to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.78,0:32:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}因为我之前一直失魂落魄\Nsince I haven't been myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.21,0:32:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}什么事\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.46,0:32:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我忘了要感谢你\NI've forgotten to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.05,0:32:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}还有些别的事\NThere's somethin' else as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.23,0:32:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}是关于埃兰的\NIt's about Elam.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.26,0:32:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你一直想谈谈他\NI know you've wanted to talk about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.40,0:32:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}听别人说  他\NFrom what people say, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.36,0:32:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他并不一直是我知道的那种人\Nhe wasn't always the man I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.81,0:32:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不  他以前不是的\NNo, he wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.40,0:32:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我现在知道了\NI know that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.23,0:32:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也知道你爱他\NAnd you loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.30,0:32:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想让你知道我相信他想念的\NThen I want you to know that I believe it was you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.88,0:32:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那人是你\Nhe was thinkin' of.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.57,0:32:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}找寻的那人也是你\NAnd lookin' for.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.33,0:33:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道  我知道\NI know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.05,0:33:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他逮捕了我们重要的修路人手\NHe's arrested our key railroad men.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.18,0:33:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}都用的是莫须有的或很早以前的罪行\NAll on trumped up charges or crimes long forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.82,0:33:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我们要如何应对\NWhat exactly are we doin' about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.28,0:33:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要做我之前就应该做的事\NI'll do what I should've done before:
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.07,0:33:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我要任命你为铁路警察总长\NI'll make you chief of railroad police,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.28,0:33:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}拥有赎回我们劳工的权利\Nwith authority to reclaim our workforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.09,0:33:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}去要求他们放人\NInsist they be released!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.32,0:33:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}铁路警徽对坎贝尔没有用\NRailroad badge won't mean nothin' to Campbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.01,0:33:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他是联邦政府的人\NHe's federal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.16,0:33:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他的警徽对铁路也没用\NSo is the railroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.15,0:33:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}妈的  我需要你  博汉南\NDamn it, I need you, Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.14,0:33:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我需要你的枪\NI need your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.69,0:33:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我发现你已经不再佩枪了\NI see you aren't even wearing one anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.24,0:33:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}对它失去兴趣了\NLost my taste for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.43,0:33:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你他妈还真会挑时间扮圣人啊\NWell, you picked one hell of a time to turn saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.06,0:33:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你被捕了\NYou are under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.22,0:34:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}罪名是谋杀联邦法警德怀特·海柯德\NFor the murder of Dwight Heckard federal marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.55,0:34:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你是新任法警吗\NYou're the new marshal?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.86,0:34:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我自己也是大吃一惊\NYou know, it surprised the hell out of me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.00,0:34:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}别碰我\NTake your hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.50,0:34:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不用给他戴手铐\NHe don't need to be cuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.69,0:34:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他要是反抗  倒是帮了我大忙\NHe'd be doin' me a favor if he puts up a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.15,0:34:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你也是  博汉南\NYou too, Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.98,0:34:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如我所言  博汉南  挑得真是时候\NLike I said, Bohannon, one hell of a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.11,0:34:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}进去吧  光鲜绅士\NIn you go, fancy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.72,0:35:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这里充满了主的平和\NThe lord's peace is upon this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.53,0:35:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我感受到了  兄弟\NI feel it, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.85,0:35:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}既然我们旅行至此休息\NWhile we rest here from travel...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.06,0:35:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你能否告诉我你到底是谁\Nyou may tell me who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.95,0:35:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我知道你不是达森\NI know you are not Dutson.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.56,0:35:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错\NMm, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.19,0:35:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我叫安德森\NMy name is Anderson.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.20,0:35:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}有一天我偶然目睹了悲剧的一幕\NI came upon a tragic scene one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.74,0:35:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}达森主教和他的妻子孩子被印第安人杀死\NBishop Dutson, his wife and child lying slaughtered
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.31,0:35:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}陈尸河边\Nby Indians beside a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.76,0:35:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}当我为他们做祷告时  我感受到了神启\NAs I prayed over them, I received a message--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.63,0:35:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来自天父的信息\NMessage from heavenly father--
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.96,0:36:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉我应当顶替这个可怜人的身份\NThat I should take this unfortunate man's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.74,0:36:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}完成他的使命\Nand do his bidden work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.37,0:36:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果我做错了\NIf I have done wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.50,0:36:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你现在还在跟我说谎就是错的\NYou have done wrong by lying to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.35,0:36:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}天父赋予了我明辨是非的洞察力\NHeavenly father endowed me with the spirit of discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.61,0:36:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}重新说\NBegin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.87,0:36:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我发誓\NI swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.23,0:36:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我是个摩门教徒\Nthat I am mormon
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.96,0:36:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我的信仰十分坚定\Nand my faith is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.22,0:36:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那达森一家是怎么回事\NAnd what then of the Dutsons?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.83,0:36:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我发现他们的时候\NWhen I found them...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.24,0:37:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他们还活着\Nthey were alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.75,0:37:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我再说一次  那是上帝的指示\NI say again, it was a sign from god.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.20,0:37:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他的意志\NHis will
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.32,0:37:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}告诉我应该夺走他们俗世的性命\Nthat I should take their earthly lives
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.04,0:37:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}然后顶替达森的名字\Nand d-drape myself in Dutson's name
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.42,0:37:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和肉身\Nand person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.67,0:37:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}之后  我竭尽全力\NThereafter, I did all I could to--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.93,0:37:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}侍奉他\Nto honor him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.69,0:37:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在史密斯保卫站想尽一切办法\NIn every way at Fort Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.32,0:37:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我现在说的一切都是真的\NEverything I have said now is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.76,0:37:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很感激我有幸被指引\NI'm thankful that my path has led me to--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.59,0:37:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}获得神圣的权利  去协助...\Nto the sacred privilege of aiding in...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.92,0:37:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}协助你的工作\Naiding in your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.62,0:37:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我相信你很懊悔\NI do believe in your remorse,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.23,0:38:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}也相信你在寻求宽恕\Nand that you seek forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.44,0:38:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}太好了\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.61,0:38:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.87,0:38:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.23,0:38:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错  没错\NI do. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.09,0:38:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}没错\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.73,0:38:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那你到底叫什么名字\NAnd what is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.01,0:38:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.65,0:38:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我叫托尔·刚德森\NI am Thor Gundersen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.50,0:38:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来自挪威\NOf Norway.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.19,0:38:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}那么\NWell...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.81,0:38:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}来自挪威的托尔·刚德森\NThor Gundersen of Norway.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.43,0:38:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你可以和我走\NYou may go forward with me
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.48,0:38:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}重新开始生活\Nand begin life again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.57,0:39:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}但是我们要去哪\NBut where shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.65,0:39:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}时间自会揭晓\NTime will reveal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.52,0:39:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我在夏安镇很少有喜欢的东西\NFew things I find pleasant in Cheyenne.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.26,0:39:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这红酒算一个\NBut this wine's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.71,0:39:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你还喜欢什么\NWhat else?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.90,0:39:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}喝酒时坐在你对面\NSittin' across from you while I drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.55,0:39:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我同意\NI agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.26,0:39:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}酒的确好喝\NAbout the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.91,0:39:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在\NNow...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.41,0:39:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我没想到会在这里遇到你这样的女士\NYou are not the kind of lady I expected to find out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.99,0:39:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}为什么像你这样久经世故的东海岸女子\NHow is it that an east coast sophisticate like yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.43,0:39:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}会沦落到边疆城镇\Nends up in a frontier town
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.38,0:39:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}和大话家杜兰特\NSurrounded by charlatans like Durant,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.35,0:39:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}流氓米奇·麦克吉尼斯\NRuffians like Mickey McGinnes...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.77,0:39:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}以及被解职的南方佬博汉南在一起\NAnd a defrocked Johnny Reb like Bohannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.87,0:40:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你忘说西德尼·斯诺了\NI notice you forgot to mention Sidney Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.84,0:40:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个枪击商店\NHow does a man who shoots up a store
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.76,0:40:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}射杀男孩的人  怎么会戴上法警徽章\Nand kills a young boy end up wearing a Marshal's badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.26,0:40:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你为什么把徽章给他\NAnd how do you justify giving it to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.09,0:40:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}问得好  埃里森女士\NGood question, Miss Ellison.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.86,0:40:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}博汉南先生\NMr. Bohannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.57,0:40:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你打扰我们用餐了\NYou're interrupting our dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.49,0:40:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我想听到你的回答\NI aim to hear your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.47,0:40:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}一个被格兰特任命  致力恢复法律和秩序的人\NHow's a man appointed by Grant to bring law and order
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.35,0:40:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}怎么会把徽章给西德尼·斯诺这样的疯狗\Nput a badge on a mad dog like Sidney Snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.30,0:40:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}他就是疯狗  我们都知道\NAnd that's what he is, we both know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.91,0:40:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我很幸运能招入他这样的人\NI'm just lucky I had a man like him to put a badge on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.60,0:40:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}这个镇子的暴力已经夺走了我的两位法警\NI've lost two marshals to violence in this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.60,0:40:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}不用再失去更多人  我便已经明白\NAnd I don't need to lose more to know that I'm a long way
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.35,0:40:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}在这里不能用和平手段重塑法律与秩序\Nfrom being able to use peaceful means to bring "Law and order,"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.65,0:40:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}正如你所说\NAs you put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.21,0:40:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我觉得新法警的手段\NI think my new marshal's methods
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.34,0:40:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}很适合这里\Nexactly fit the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.09,0:40:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}西德尼带来的不是法律和秩序\NWhat Sidney's bringing ain't law and order,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.33,0:40:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}人都被抓进监狱了  我没法铺铁路\Nand I can't build a railroad with them men in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.71,0:40:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}铁路和其他的事必须等等\NThen the railroad and everything else will have to wait
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.24,0:41:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}直到我驯服这座镇子\Nuntil I bring this town to heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.84,0:41:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我说得明白点吧  坎贝尔先生\NLet me spell it out for you, Mr. Campbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.46,0:41:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}放了囚犯们\NRelease them prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.24,0:41:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我只说一次\NI'm only askin' you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.33,0:41:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}如果这是威胁  我就当没听见\NIf that's a threat, I didn't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.79,0:41:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}现在  你能让女士和我继续用餐了吗\NNow would you let this lady and me go on with our dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.77,0:41:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}你要记住\NYou remember:
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.84,0:41:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}我先礼貌地问过你\NI asked you as a gentleman first.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.60,0:41:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\shad1\4a&H80&\b0}埃里森女士\NMiss Ellison.

